ARTWORK:
    /Tilesets
        The art located in the folder Tilesets is a modified version of 
        https://szadiart.itch.io/rogue-fantasy-catacombs by Szadi Art 
        (https://szadiart.itch.io/)
            Public domain and free to use, personal or commercial. 
            Credit is not required but appreciated. You can edit, 
            but not resell the asset pack (original or changed).

    /sprites
        fireball.png made by #ScagHound 
        https://opengameart.org/content/fireball-flying-through-the-air
        The rest is made by myself.
        All Artwork located in the folder sprites is marked with CC0 1.0. 
        To view a copy of this license, visit 
        https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

